        "des": "<style>\n.size-guide {\n  padding: 80px 6%;\n  background: #fbf7f2;\n  font-family: Georgia, serif;\n  color: #6f6a63;\n}\n\n.container {\n  max-width: 1200px;\n  margin: auto;\n}\n\n.title {\n  text-align: center;\n  font-size: 46px;\n  margin-bottom: 60px;\n}\n\n/* Image Section */\n.guide-row {\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 60px;\n  margin-bottom: 80px;\n}\n\n.guide-row img {\n  width: 50%;\n  border-radius: 6px;\n}\n\n.guide-text {\n  width: 50%;\n}\n\n.guide-text h3 {\n  font-size: 32px;\n  margin-bottom: 10px;\n}\n\n.guide-text p {\n  line-height: 1.7;\n}\n\n/* Chart */\n.chart h2 {\n  font-size: 34px;\n  margin-bottom: 10px;\n}\n\n.chart hr {\n  border: none;\n  border-top: 1px solid #b08b74;\n  margin-bottom: 30px;\n}\n\n.steps {\n  padding-left: 20px;\n  margin-bottom: 40px;\n}\n\n.steps li {\n  margin-bottom: 10px;\n  line-height: 1.6;\n}\n\n.table-wrap {\n  overflow-x: auto;\n}\n\ntable {\n  border-collapse: collapse;\n  width: 100%;\n  min-width: 900px;\n}\n\nth, td {\n  border: 1px solid #6f6a63;\n  padding: 14px;\n  text-align: center;\n  font-size: 14px;\n}\n\nth {\n  font-weight: normal;\n}\n\n/* Mobile */\n@media (max-width: 768px) {\n  .guide-row {\n    flex-direction: column;\n  }\n\n  .guide-row img,\n  .guide-text {\n    width: 100%;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n}\n</style>\n\n<section class=\"size-guide\">\n  <div class=\"container\">\n\n    <h2 class=\"title\">Ring Size Guide</h2>\n\n    <!-- Image + Content -->\n    <div class=\"guide-row\">\n      <img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/714hJdaDeZL._SX695_.jpg\" alt=\"Ring Size Guide\">\n\n      <div class=\"guide-text\">\n        <h3>Measure Your Ring Size</h3>\n        <p>The most accurate way is to measure your finger using a strip of paper or thread and match it with the chart below.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Chart -->\n    <div class=\"chart\">\n      <h2>Ring Size Chart</h2>\n      <hr>\n\n      <ul class=\"steps\">\n        <li>Cut a thin strip of paper or thread.</li>\n        <li>Wrap it around your finger.</li>\n        <li>Mark where it meets.</li>\n        <li>Measure with a ruler (mm).</li>\n      </ul>\n\n      <div class=\"table-wrap\">\n        <table>\n          <tr>\n            <th>Diameter (mm)</th>\n            <td>14.05</td>\n            <td>14.25</td>\n            <td>14.45</td>\n            <td>14.65</td>\n            <td>14.86</td>\n            <td>15.04</td>\n            <td>15.27</td>\n            <td>15.53</td>\n            <td>15.70</td>\n            <td>15.90</td>\n            <td>16.10</td>\n            <td>16.30</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <th>Ring Size</th>\n            <td>3</td>\n            <td>3¼</td>\n            <td>3½</td>\n            <td>3¾</td>\n            <td>4</td>\n            <td>4¼</td>\n            <td>4½</td>\n            <td>4¾</td>\n            <td>5</td>\n            <td>5¼</td>\n            <td>5½</td>\n            <td>5¾</td>\n          </tr>\n        </table>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</section>",
